decks.notes: The main focus of this deck is to control the game through powerful counterspells, removal spells, and card advantage. Ertai Resurrected serves as the commander and provides a solid control strategy with the ability to counter spells by sacrificing creatures. The deck includes a variety of efficient removal spells like Fatal Push, Drown in the Loch, and Toxic Deluge to deal with threats on the board. It also includes powerful card draw spells such as Brainstorm, Demonic Tutor, and Mystic Confluence to maintain card advantage. The mana base is optimized with fetch lands and dual lands to ensure consistent mana production. Overall, the deck aims to outvalue and outlast opponents through efficient control tactics and card advantage.

The main idea of this deck is to overwhelm the opponent with aggressive creatures and spells, supported by disruptive and controlling elements to maintain tempo and control the board. Ghyrson Starn, Kelermorph leads the charge, backed up by cards like True-Name Nemesis, Goblin Bombardment, and Brazen Borrower. The deck focuses on using efficient removal spells like Lightning Bolt and Chain Lightning to clear the way for its threats, while also utilizing disruptive spells like Force of Will and Spell Pierce to protect its own game plan. The mana base is designed to support a fast and consistent aggression, allowing the deck to apply pressure early and maintain it throughout the game.
